    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are a good start but they're a bit high-level. my students need more depth to actually win rounds. can you expand on the \"national sovereignty\" point? specifically, how do they use the concept of a social contract to justify why strict enforcement is a moral necessity for a functional state? i want them to have that philosophical weight behind their arguments.",
